<major-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2011-02-16.0.mh" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-11/wa0216.htm">Written Answers Wednesday 16 February 2011</major-heading>

<major-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2011-02-16.1.mh" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-11/wa0216.htm">Scottish Executive</major-heading>

<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2011-02-16.S3W-39218.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-11/wa0216.htm#1">Child Welfare</minor-heading>

<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2011-02-16.S3W-39218.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80291" speakername="Robert Brown (Glasgow) (LD)" spid="S3W-39218" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-11/wa0216.htm#1">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive for what reason the report of the short-life working group on school meal and clothing grant provision was not published until 22 months after it was completed.</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2011-02-16.S3W-39218.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80331" speakername="Adam Ingram" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-11/wa0216.htm#1">

  <p>As noted in the answer to question S3W-38465 on 26 January 2011, consideration of the report took place in the context of the Draft Budget 2011-12. The report was then published once ministers concluded consideration of the recommendations.</p>

</reply>


<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2011-02-16.S3W-39400.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-11/wa0216.htm#2">Fisheries</minor-heading>

<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2011-02-16.S3W-39400.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80364" speakername="Nanette Milne (North East Scotland) (Con)" spid="S3W-39400" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-11/wa0216.htm#2">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive how many people have been employed in the fishing industry in each year since 2007.</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2011-02-16.S3W-39400.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80340" speakername="Richard Lochhead" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-11/wa0216.htm#2">

